  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, this created a great deal of concern in the school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other teachers were upset because, up until that time, I was the best in the class.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the director of the school, who was a reasonable man, Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Palfi, ?] asked him that, what's happening?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told the director that he could not really give me any mark because I did not write any of the papers and he put them on the Saturdays because it's more comfortable for him to have the paper on the Saturday and to have Sunday to correct it.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The director, whose son was a classmate and a friend of mine, told him that you can have this paper written on Fridays, and you still can correct it on Sundays.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At which point he-- he had the next Hungarian paper on a Thursday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I failed that paper because he underlined every n and m that I wrote, that, you know, the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] letter was not tall enough at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he counted all the n's and m's in the paper, and there was about 35 of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So with 35 errors in a paper, nobody can pass.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I failed that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to him and asked me if he would write me a sample n and m-- from here on, I will write it correctly.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- next paper was a German paper on a Friday, and I failed that, too, but the n's and m's were excellent, because I wrote it exactly as he showed me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the s and zed were not wavy enough for him, and I failed on that.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
